{"tid":501912,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"未來日記真係幾正","createTime":"2017-12-17T11:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T10:06:36.000Z","uid":30673,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e823678f2b1dfb0b40d58216a8ca21fb4be21342","tid":501912,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"動畫咁就又過6,7年<br />\n初初未知病嬌為何物 以為女主只係痴情少少<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DDqRfVYVYAE4iDZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDDqRfVYVYAE4iDZ.jpg&h=3e3c01f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點知越黎越痴媽根 每集都插少少好唔妥 唔解唔得既恐怖位<br />\n<img src=\"http://blog-imgs-46.fc2.com/c/h/i/chiqfudoki/20120313055006853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-46.fc2.com%2Fc%2Fh%2Fi%2Fchiqfudoki%2F20120313055006853.jpg&h=a60947ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://suntzuanime.files.wordpress.com/2012/02/ting.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsuntzuanime.files.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F02%2Fting.png&h=ba9f2de3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係新一集即刻好似無野發生過咁 連住睇不安程度真係推到頂<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-001.west.edge.storage-yahoo.jp/res/blog-61-d5/tebuku/folder/1044096/47/29707847/img_11?1330972461\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-001.west.edge.storage-yahoo.jp%2Fres%2Fblog-61-d5%2Ftebuku%2Ffolder%2F1044096%2F47%2F29707847%2Fimg_11%3F1330972461&h=637d9031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開信封位呢幕真係嚇到爆屎 <br />\n中期開始用完懸疑恐怖就落緊湊刺激<br />\n敵人越黎越有理念衝突 女主身份一步一步揭故<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/8c/c2/be/8cc2bed0e45e756d91b545cba25e65d6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F8c%2Fc2%2Fbe%2F8cc2bed0e45e756d91b545cba25e65d6.gif&h=5677d4c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zOJqjST.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzOJqjST.gif&h=e1dd2ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n殺哂所有人先發現原來死人無得翻生 秋瀨本埋條命出黎講個真相比男主聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://24.media.tumblr.com/3fc156047e6801b09a5cf2c257a51033/tumblr_mjolm9peZk1qcre7so1_r1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F24.media.tumblr.com%2F3fc156047e6801b09a5cf2c257a51033%2Ftumblr_mjolm9peZk1qcre7so1_r1_500.gif&h=e15618cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過埋尾就唔係太掂 太普通對唔返之前部份咁高質<br />\n最後bbq大家唔洗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cab57144d79d3e19c33071e6d03292bfd671d0e","tid":501912,"uid":34293,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:06:28.000Z","msg":"big order完美超越"},{"pid":"e0a95fe62804ecd6a6086e34e50462258a278ebc","tid":501912,"uid":31585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:06:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>big order完美超越</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704a8792220144e6163565e60b75826cd25a8146","tid":501912,"uid":828,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"好想俾由乃斬"},{"pid":"65d28defcde12ed7004f55ef10e58eeedd1d7d24","tid":501912,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:09:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e50afcb9bdea1fa1e056d2689fa9fd1335d6a9a3","tid":501912,"uid":127244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"俾你講完之後即刻上HULU開嚟睇"},{"pid":"ef3f4486c82c8239d6a3121e74786366c710a221","tid":501912,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾你講完之後即刻上HULU開嚟睇</blockquote><br />\n劇透左既話唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c547ec599d6a512efacb1ba53b05781f9540f4b","tid":501912,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:12:31.000Z","msg